41:44.200 --> 41:46.191
- How many people
have you killed?

41:51.970 --> 41:55.076
- Many more than your father.

42:02.950 --> 42:05.680
- Are you going to kill me?

42:07.690 --> 42:09.851
- I'm so sorry, Abigail.

